summary: Dillon and Clay over at One List One Life are working hard to Live For Another and asked on Reddit for some help in raising...
body: Dillon and Clay over at One List One Life are working hard to Live For Another and asked on Reddit for some help in raising awareness for a cinema that they are renting out to play a private screening of Avengers: Endgame and hopefully get some of the cast to shoot a private video for cancer patients and sick kids. I don’t have many followers at all but I thought I should at least be a single voice in the crowd that’s trying to make this happen.
